_sText:
This map took me about a day to make. It consists of a gun game arena that holds up to 40 players, numerous amount of props, with a scenic background and quality. The arena is high in the air, that's why there is a volumetric fog hovering on the ground, highly great detail.

I would like to thank the team, and those who inspired me to make this map.

If you are interested in my other map: castle_base_b2 feel free to view over that as well.

Thanks for downloading and have fun!
Duck of source development team

P.S.- If you are interested in viewing the official souce development mapping team website: http://halomoddingsite.com/meteoraCSS/index.php

Also I have some tutorials on mapping that you can watch if you're interested in: http://www.firedraco21.proboards102.com/index.cgi?board=cssmapmakingmodding
